      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must pass standard benchmark verification cases relevant to rotating machinery flow.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent verified against Taylor-Couette flow and lid-driven cavity benchmarks. Published verification suite results confirm second-order spatial accuracy. Achieved level 2 exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
    },
