      "rationale": "Three-mesh Richardson extrapolation performed at 2.1M, 5.8M, and 14.2M cell counts. GCI for relative hemolysis index = 3.7%, satisfying the 5% acceptance criterion. Asymptotic convergence ratio 0.98 confirms grid-independent solution."
